snippet.textDisplay:
In my childhood, I used to watch this serial Balika Vadhu, and whenever this song played, I loved it so much! I really, really, really loved it.
Then, I searched for it many times on YouTube, but I couldn’t find it. Maybe because I didn’t type the  words correctly..😅

Since I’m from Nepal, I don’t understand the lyrics properly that what does this words mean to be..But I got the vibe with this song.🤘🤘   And finally, I’m so happy that I got this song today 2025/02/01 😊❤❤
 
Enjoy the song everyone 🥰
snippet.textOriginal:
In my childhood, I used to watch this serial Balika Vadhu, and whenever this song played, I loved it so much! I really, really, really loved it.
Then, I searched for it many times on YouTube, but I couldn’t find it. Maybe because I didn’t type the  words correctly..😅

Since I’m from Nepal, I don’t understand the lyrics properly that what does this words mean to be..But I got the vibe with this song.🤘🤘   And finally, I’m so happy that I got this song today 2025/02/01 😊❤❤
 
Enjoy the song everyone 🥰
